                <span style="background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 2rem; padding: 0.2rem 1rem; font-weight: 600;">🧾 легенда</span>
                <span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #d1fae5; border-radius: 50%;"></span> ключ НЕ нужен</span>
